q = filter q by 'RecordTypeName' != "Household";q = order q by ('SnapshotDate_Year' asc,'SnapshotDate_Month' asc,'SnapshotDate_Day' asc);q = foreach q generate 'SnapshotDate_Year','SnapshotDate_Week', 'SnapshotDate_Quarter', 'Id', 'SnapshotDate_Month', 'SnapshotDate_Day', 'AUM' as 'BALANCE';q = group q by ('Id','SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}});q = foreach q generate 'SnapshotDate_Year',{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}, last('BALANCE') as 'BALANCE';q = group q by ('SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}});q = foreach q generate 'SnapshotDate_Year' + "~~~" + {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}} as 'SnapshotDate_Year~~~{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}', sum('BALANCE') as 'sum_BALANCE';q = order q by 'SnapshotDate_Year~~~{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}' asc;q = limit q 2000;

Wallet_Share_Trend_1.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.FscDemoFinancialAccountSnapshot.FullyQualifiedName}";managed = load "${App.Datasets.FscDemoAccountSnapshot.FullyQualifiedName}";managed = filter managed by 'RecordTypeName' != "Household";managed = order managed by ('SnapshotDate_Year' asc,'SnapshotDate_Month' asc,'SnapshotDate_Day' asc);managed = foreach managed generate 'SnapshotDate_Year','SnapshotDate_Week', 'SnapshotDate_Quarter', 'Id', 'SnapshotDate_Month', 'SnapshotDate_Day', 'AUM' as 'Balance';managed = group managed by ('Id','SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}});managed = foreach managed generate 'SnapshotDate_Year',{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}, last('Balance') as 'Balance';q = order q by ('SnapshotDate_Year' asc,'SnapshotDate_Month' asc,'SnapshotDate_Day' asc);q = foreach q generate 'SnapshotDate_Year','SnapshotDate_Week', 'SnapshotDate_Quarter', 'Id', 'SnapshotDate_Month', 'SnapshotDate_Day', 'Balance' as 'Balance';q = group q by ('Id','SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}});q = foreach q generate 'SnapshotDate_Year',{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}, last('Balance') as 'Balance';q = group q by ('SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}) left, managed by ('SnapshotDate_Year', {{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}});q = foreach q generate q.'SnapshotDate_Year' + "~~~" + q.{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}} as 'SnapshotDate_Year~~~{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}', round(sum(managed.'Balance')/sum(q.'Balance'),4) as 'sum_Wallet Share';q = order q by 'SnapshotDate_Year~~~{{cell(Group_By__Time__1.selection, 0, "value").asObject()}}' asc;q = limit q 2000;
